cs.SY, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.SE 

The paper deals with the problem of controlling a vehicle's longitudinal and lateral motions, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The use of "intelligent" controllers suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI) techniques. The simulation results and the use of Matlab and SiVIC/RTMaps platforms indicate the involvement of software engineering (cs.SE) and machine learning (cs.LG) sub-categories.
